p: The screening of the phytochemical compounds from the oil was performed by docking them on selected binding pockets of SARS-CoV-2 proteins and ranked based on their binding energies. The multiple docking of the ligands and proteins was done with Autodock Vina in PyRx software (Tsao et al. 2020; Johnson et al. 2020). The molecular docking results were organized on an Excel spreadsheet, and the Heat Map of the data was viewed using the Conditional Formatting function.
